Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage still Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must break through this airborne alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And discover the trick behind the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a child but has the brain of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To join in a TV program broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of a talk between professional baseball player\NNose Toshizou and sports reporter Motoyama Masaharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We rushed to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in Naha Airport,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And headed toward Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}'s jogging area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Jaguar uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't that Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the ambulance and the police fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The police?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naha City Police Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway... Please catch that murderer as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The monster who destroyed my friend's\Ndream of beating the Japan national record.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man is the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Course Without Protest. Part Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You looked so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was shocked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What happened just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow the car keys, Teranishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot something in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What... What is it, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Miyazaki Hotel key-card that you were carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not a one-time use card, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you return it to the front\Ndesk when you checked out of the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... I haven't checked out of the room yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have another interview\Nprogram in Miyazaki the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you originally also have\Nan interview in Okinawa tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Returning to Miyazaki Hotel and then coming buck to\NOkinawa again... Isn't the plane ticket a little wasteful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to know ahead of time that\Ntomorrow's interview would be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Nah... It seems that I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, why did everyone come to the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... They're going to investigate the scene again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r} fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just making sure we didn't\Nmiss anything. Normal procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just now, you used your left hand to catch the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was the number 4\Npitcher on my high school baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you take that small road to go\Naround on the way to Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}'s hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because during that time, the\Nbigger road would have been very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, even though it's farther in distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smaller road is faster to get to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran should have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that he didn't check out of the hotel room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer is Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who killed Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a shortcut in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've done a brief search of the surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 9:30 am, when Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r} was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one had come near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's no witness,\Nno murder weapon, and no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take your time, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is still a lot of time left\Nbefore our plane leaves for Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can find some\Nevidence the murderer forgot to get rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this brat talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Could I go eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't had anything since arriving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting here. Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's all take my car and go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I come to this restaurant quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's grab a quick meal\Nand return to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a call from the TV station producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll go into the restaurant first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you're finished with your call,\Nlock the door and come in to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Motoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The phone ringed once just now, I checked\Nthe call record and it said it was you, Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wondered if there's any new\Ndevelopment in Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}'s case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... I probably pressed\Nthe wrong button on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anything comes up, I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking that\NMotoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really is a famous detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking about how he knew Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}\Nwas murdered by just seeing him lying down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he heard from\NNose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r} that he was being threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about what Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said to me in the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're going, kid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're going, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you call him a famous detective because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because at that time, I wasn't\Nnear Uncle Kogorou or Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was talking to the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how did he know that I came with Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an incredible deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now... Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the first time we saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well... Let's talk while we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Empty spaces are over at...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though' there's empty space,\Nwe can't get to it walking straight in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... We'll go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! I'm already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was faster to take the farther way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as I destroy this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one will know my crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you help me get the schedule in my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot the time for our return flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friend asked me to buy some souvenirs from Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to go ahead and buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you tell everyone not to wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I'm done,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just get some bread or something to eat\Nand meet you guys back at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naha Airport Parking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're in good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't your best friend just\Ndie? Quite a fast recovery you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What... What kind of idiocy are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have on alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose was killed at around 9:30 in the morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sitting on a plane from Miyazaki\Nto Okinawa that arrived at 9:50, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, that's the only plane\Nthat comes from Miyazaki to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a live broadcast at Miyazaki last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how could I possibly kill Nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true. It's impossible if you come directly from Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you go around and come through Tokyo to get here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's possible for you to get to\NOkinawa before 9:30 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like avoiding the busy\Nmain street by taking a longer way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It lets you reach your destination faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking the 8:35 pm plane from Miyazaki to Tokyo first...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:37.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And then if you take the 6:35\Nplane in the next morning to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to arrive at 9:20 am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, using a pre-rented car...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went directly from the airport to\Nambush and kill Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r} who was out jogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you only needed to return\Nto Naha Airport's exit before 9:50 am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretending that you just got to\NOkinawa and appeared before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait... Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came out of the arrival\Nterminal of Naha Airport after 9:50 am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I arrived on the 9:20 airplane...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And left the airport once already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I get into the arrival terminal again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you bring us here because you\Nsaid you knew who the murderer was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly... There's no other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the people at that restaurant earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were they all looking at us so weirdly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've all entered the restaurant and found a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we didn't order any food and left immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got hungry, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want my orange juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Entering the restaurant but not\Nordering any food and leaving immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Naha Airport's arrival\Nterminal and the departure terminal are interconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only need to get a ticket\Nto enter the departure terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And without boarding the plane, you\Ncan still come out of the arrival terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that! That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that... The fact that you didn't\Ncheck out of your room in Miyazaki is also suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you took the plane from\NMiyazaki to Okinawa this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've been able to check\Nout of your hotel room in Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since you knew you'd\Nhave on interview in Okinawa tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying here for the night would be more logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't do that because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd already left Miyazaki last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking the night plane to Tokyo which is farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evidence. Where's your evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we have evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't we, Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll leave the rest to the famous detective then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, why don't you drink some orange juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For his plan, Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was on\Nthe 931 plane from Tokyo to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, we were sitting on that same plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the flight, my daughter\Nspilled a container full of tennis balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which were recovered with the help of nearby passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among these passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was someone who caught\Nthe tennis ball with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very suspicious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that be Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't he right-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's used to catching balls with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, in his old job, he had to protect his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, without thinking, he used his left hand to catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, would you please take it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing you stole from Ran's\Nbag and hid in your inside pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who took the title of the king\Nof new players and the savior of the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ex-professional baseball\Nplayer... Motoyama Masaharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What... What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sweating...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it getting warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drink some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the fingerprints that were\Nimprinted on the tennis ball at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the unshakable evidence\Nthat points to you as the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I may have said it that way, but actually that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hard tennis balls with their furry surfaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make it really hard to find fingerprints on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if there were some imprinted...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can only prove that you and I were on the same plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It cannot prove that you are Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senshu{\r}'s murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I let you steal the tennis\Nball container and go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that maybe you'd lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the place where you hid the murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the blood-splattered clothes that you wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is definitely unshakable proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To see the truth only by him catching the ball\Nwith his left hand... no wonder you're famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, it was when we supposedly met\NMotoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for the first time in the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He called this brat here to come\Nwith us. That's when it came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Maybe Motoyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} met\Nus before we met in the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And saw us together somewhere before."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would've guessed that this\Nhyperactive brat wound actually be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it would've been better if I\Nhad put him to sleep with the stun needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost my pitcher spot because of my habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, I dug a grave for myself with my habit as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the end of the first season when I received the\Ntitles of King of Newcomers and savior of the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You have a bad habit when you pitch."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked my pose with detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the point where I became paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still... I couldn't find the bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, because of all the over\Ntraining I did, I sprained my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That when I retired,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nose's attitude changed towards me.\NHe even got me a job at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw the unedited tape of a sports program by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the question was finally answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there any other topic that you feel is worth mentioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us something, Nose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way to break a young pitcher is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only have to whisper into his ears that he has a\Nbad pitching habit, and then he'll self-destruct for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please cut this part... It's not good broadcasting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, someone else told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I didn't have a bad habit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet, I was still grateful to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he become the savior of the Jaguar team after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I supported him like he was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel unfair and ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To stop him from making the Japan notional record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using Hideyoshi's counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the real person to break the national\Nrecord and have worldwide fame should have been me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make him realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. No matter what you do, you'll never\Nhave the right to break Japan's national record.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's regrettable that you were deceived...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the pitcher is a team's last hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may lose the game, and be\Nyelled at for no reason by everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the next game, they have to recover, and return\Nonce again to the pitcher's spot as if nothing's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone like you, who could kill\Nsomeone else for stepping in your way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would never be able to sustain the hope of on entire team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm the one who wants to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of your doing something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was finally able to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take time to think about where you went wrong in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you want to say just then, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the wind I sometimes smile, sometimes cry, and sometimes fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us are just like this standing in front of our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our dream is sure to be somewhere in the unknown future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The colors of the seasons, always repeating let us experience a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:23:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look upon the side of your sleepy face with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying in that moment, this becomes our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard on getting this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can give it to her now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the last of the\Nlast autographs out there right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a super rare collector's item! I'm rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a poisonous black widow spider, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to leave the scene the\Nway it is until the police arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou said...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is very suspicious that only the cure\Nfor the black widow's poison is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: Deadly Poisonous Spider Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.78,0:24:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.01,0:24:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.86,0:24:51.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next Time, it will finally be in new school term again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.02,0:24:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait in excited anticipation for the next episode
